# Accent icon boxes (Mandatory)

Full contract: [Accent-Icon-Box-Standard.md](../../docs/02_FLUTTER_MIGRATION/Accent-Icon-Box-Standard.md)

## When editing list rows with module accent icons

1. **Use `VitAccentIconBox`** — no page-local `_AccentIcon` or inline `DecoratedBox` accent copies.
2. **Size** — `AppSpacing.accentIconBoxSize` (34px) everywhere; no `discoveryAccentIconBox` / `dcaScheduleAccentIconBox` for new UI.
3. **Tokens** — `accentIconFillAlpha`, `accentIconBorderAlpha`, `AppRadii.mdRadius`, `AppSpacing.iconMd`.
4. **Muted rows** — pass `muted: true` for disabled/inactive states (surface2, no accent border).

## Verify before batch complete

```bash
cd flutter_app
flutter test test/shared/widgets/vit_shared_widgets_test.dart --name "VitAccentIconBox"
flutter test test/quality/accent_icon_box_guardrail_test.dart --reporter=compact
```
